textAnnotations.description:
INA'S VEGETARIAN PHIL-
OSOPHY WAS SIMPLE...
THEN, ONE DAY, THERE IN HER
ALL-ORGANIC, VEGAN BURRITO
IT'S.. .ITS.
RICK PERRY!
I NEVER EAT
ANYTHING
WITH A FACE
I CAN'T EAT
RICK PERRY!
THIS FLAPJACK
IS MITT ROMNEY..THOSE ARE
ONLY WITH ZIIY
LATER, AT DINNER,
THIS BEAN
CURD!
BUBBLES
LOOKS LIKE
HERMAN
CAIN!!
JUST FLIP IT,
AND THERE IS
NO FACE.
IT'S
INEDIBLE!
AND FINALLY
AT BREAKFAST !
